11 Step 8. Inspect output files
After the run finishes, check the output directory:
cd /scratch/USERNAME/structure/
ls -lh ${DATASET}_results_${MAXK}pop_${REPS}rep
A complete run should contain output files for each K value and replicate. With -K 25 and -R 10, the expected number of STRUCTURE runs is:
25 K values × 10 replicates = 250 STRUCTURE runs
If some runs failed, check:

the SLURM .err file;
the Structure_threader log;
whether MAXPOPS in mainparams matches -K;
whether NUMINDS, NUMLOCI, PLOIDY, and MISSING are correct;
whether the .str file has UNIX line endings.
